OL,3,CStarmer calls on European leaders to
OL,4,Cmodernise ECHR to tackle illegal
OL,5,Cmigration
OL,7,FThe prime minister has urged Europe's
OL,8,Fleaders to reform how a major human
OL,9,Frights treaty is interpreted in law to
OL,10,Ftackle illegal migration and prevent
OL,11,Fvoters from turning to "the forces
OL,12,Fthat seek to divide us".
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer and his Danish
OL,15,Fcounterpart, Mette Frederiksen, have
OL,16,Fmade a joint call on other leaders
OL,17,Facross the continent to agree on a
OL,18,F"modernisation" of how the European
OL,19,FConvention on Human Rights (ECHR) is
OL,20,Finterpreted in their countries' laws.
