OL,7,FEuropean ministers, including Deputy
OL,8,FPrime Minister David Lammy, are due to
OL,9,Fmeet in Strasbourg, France, on
OL,10,FWednesday to discuss how the treaty is
OL,11,Finterpreted in the courts.
OL,13,FIt is understood that a political
OL,14,Fdeclaration signed by the gathered
OL,15,Fministers could carry enough weight to
OL,16,Fdirectly influence how the European
OL,17,FCourt of Human Rights interprets the
OL,18,Fagreement.
