OL,7,FIn an opinion piece for the Guardian
OL,8,Fnewspaper, Starmer and Frederiksen
OL,9,Fadvocated for a tougher approach to
OL,10,Fpolicing Europe's borders as a means
OL,11,Fof winning against populist political
OL,12,Fopponents, saying they were "making
OL,13,Fthis case across Europe".
OL,15,FThe ECHR, which underpins Britain's
OL,16,FHuman Rights Act, is seen by its
OL,17,Fcritics as a major barrier to attempts
OL,18,Fto deport illegal migrants from the
OL,19,Fcountry.
