OL,7,FThe right to family life, enshrined by
OL,8,FArticle 8 of the agreement, is often
OL,9,Fused as grounds in legal cases to
OL,10,Fprevent removals.
OL,12,FThe Home Office has also said it has
OL,13,Fseen a trend of Article 3 rights,
OL,14,Fprohibiting torture, being used to
OL,15,Fhalt deportations because of claims
OL,16,Fthat migrants' healthcare needs could
OL,17,Fnot be met in their homeland.
