OL,7,FStarmer's political opponents, the
OL,8,FConservatives and Reform UK, have both
OL,9,Fsaid they would leave the ECHR if in
OL,10,Fpower.
OL,12,FThe prime minister, in his joint op-ed
OL,13,Fwith Fredriksen, acknowledged the
OL,14,F"current asylum framework was created
OL,15,Ffor another era", adding: "In a world
OL,16,Fwith mass mobility, yesterday's
OL,17,Fanswers do not work. We will always
OL,18,Fprotect those fleeing war and terror `
OL,19,Fbut the world has changed, and asylum
OL,20,Fsystems must change with it."
