OL,4,Cmodernise ECHR to tackle illegal
OL,5,Cmigration
OL,7,FDespite opponents' stated intention to
OL,8,Fleave the ECHR, Starmer's government
OL,9,Fhas insisted it will remain a member
OL,10,Fof the treaty, and has adopted a
OL,11,Fseries of hardline immigration
OL,12,Fmeasures, modelled on those
OL,13,Fspearheaded by Frederiksen's Danish
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,F"Migration must be orderly, managed
OL,17,Fand sustainable. Irregular routes
OL,18,Fshould not be the go-to option ` so we
OL,19,Fmust dismantle the human smuggling
OL,20,Fnetworks that prey on desperation.
