OL,7,F"Together, we are calling on our
OL,8,Ffriends across Europe to go further in
OL,9,Ftackling these shared challenges," the
OL,10,Ftwo leaders wrote.
OL,12,FThey continued, describing a "push for
OL,13,Fa modernisation of the interpretation
OL,14,Fof the European Convention on Human
OL,15,FRights ` so that the convention
OL,16,Fsystem, which we believe in, can
OL,17,Fevolve to reflect the challenges of
OL,18,Fthe 21st century."
