OL,3,CStarmer calls on European leaders to
OL,4,Cmodernise ECHR to tackle illegal
OL,5,Cmigration
OL,7,FIn a warning to other leaders, Starmer
OL,8,Fand Fredriksen added: "Europe has
OL,9,Ffaced big tests before and we have
OL,10,Fovercome them by acting together. Now
OL,11,Fwe must do so again. Otherwise, the
OL,12,Fforces that seek to divide us will
OL,13,Fgrow stronger.
OL,15,F"So our message is this: as
OL,16,Fresponsible, progressive governments
OL,17,Fwe will deliver the change that people
OL,18,Fare crying out for. We will control
OL,19,Four borders to protect our democracies
OL,20,F` and make our nations stronger than
OL,21,Fever in the years to come."
