OL,7,FAmnesty International UK hit out at UK
OL,8,Fplans to lead reforms of the ECHR,
OL,9,Fdescribing it as weakening protections.
OL,11,FSteve Valdez-Symonds, Amnesty
OL,12,FInternational UK's refugee and migrant
OL,13,Frights programme director, said:
OL,14,F"There is a dreadful irony in our
OL,15,FJustice Secretary working with his
OL,16,Fcounterparts to remove or reduce
OL,17,Frights on the anniversary of the
OL,18,FUniversal Declaration of Human Rights.
