OL,7,F"It shows how far we have drifted from
OL,8,Fthe moral resolve of the last century,
OL,9,Fwhen our grandparents determined that
OL,10,Fthe fact we are all born free and
OL,11,Fequal must be protected in law.
OL,13,F"Human rights were never meant to be
OL,14,Foptional or reserved for comfortable
OL,15,Fand secure times. They were designed
OL,16,Fto be a compass, our conscience, when
OL,17,Fthe politics of fear and division try
OL,18,Fto steer us wrong.
